data.description: Welcome to this lovingly cared-for two-story gem in the heart of the Fieldstone subdivision. With four cozy bedrooms and 2.5 baths, it's nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac, providing a serene retreat.  Sunlight pours into every corner, highlighting the spacious bedrooms and the inviting open living and kitchen space. You'll fall in love with the laminate flooring, and the thoughtful upgrades like Energy Star thermostats and stunning Granite Counters.  The primary bedroom, a haven of peace and privacy, graces the first floor. Upstairs, you'll find more room to spread out with a generous game and media room, alongside the secondary bedrooms.  Convenience is key, with the Westpark Tollway and Grand Parkway 99 just moments away, giving you easy access to a world of shopping, dining, and entertainment.  This home is zoned to top-rated FB-ISD schools, ensuring the best education for your kids. Plus, you can rest easy knowing there's no history of flooding.
